history.content:
161 would have no relation at all with 189.

188 isn't as related to 189 as it might sound, but it does have a section on ML at the end that could help prepare / familiarize you with 189 topics. I'd also rate 188 as an easier class than 161, which could factor into your decision given your other classes.

My other two techs are 170 and 127. I was on the waitlist for 161 and enrolled in 188, and it seems like I'll be able to get into 161, so I have to decide which one to drop. For reference, I'm interested in theory and have taken all the lower div pre requisites, also plan to take 189 next semester. Which class would fit better? Which one would fit better with 189 next semester? Any thoughts would be great.
history.subject: 161 or 188
